        "TileImage": "$($repository 04387b7a-25fa-4dec-baa0-eeff1d36ab11).Image",
        "Description": "This is it, 47.\r\rAfter your unintended visit to Romania, our analists have found that the Constant has survived, and is at the isle of sgail to tie up loose ends. Furthurmore, we have found two other visitors to the island are secretly orking with the constant to make up a plan when the constant dies. We have found this plan to be simply put that the two partners will gain full control over Providence assets, and we cannot let this happen. good luck, 47.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.",
